timeline.bodyText:
i gave the same comment on the other PR -- do we want to make it an enum?
also "truncate at user streamcut" as the enum value is confusion from the end users perspective.. what is a user streamcut?
i suggested that we use two booleans.

subscribeForRetention
acknowledge last checkpoint
and to ensure that 2 is only available to be set when 1 is true, we can use builder methods and hide the setters for individual booleans.

for example:
ReaderGroupConfigBuilder {
...
   ReadGroupConfigBuilder subscribe(boolean acknowledgeAtCheckpoints) {
       this.subscribe = true;
       this.acknowledgeAtCheckpoints = acknowledgeAtCheckpoints;
       return this;
   }
}

